dataIdInfo.idAbs: This layer contains the boundaries for California’s 58 counties. County features are derived from the US Census Bureau's 2023 TIGER/Line database and have been clipped to the coastal boundary line and designed to overlay with the California Department of Education’s (CDE) educational boundary layers.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: US Census Bureau, National Center for Educational Statistics (NCES)
